{"tid":2508674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東10歲男童當街燒4車　原因竟為「想看車爆炸飛起來」","createTime":"2021-04-29T02:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T02:47:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"12ba0dde9b0dc94be2f8c03724f28191c8244a02","tid":2508674,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"廣東陽江市近日4輛泊在路邊的車先後突然起火，警方追查後，發現事件的始作俑者竟是一名年僅10歲的男童，他到案後坦言是因在電視上看到爆炸覺得非常刺激才放火燒車，「想看車爆炸飛起來」。<br />\n<br />\n本月18日，警方獲報指石灣村舊寨有2輛汽車起火，起火部位均為小汽車車頭處。消防員接報後立即趕赴現場把火撲滅，同時警方發現距離兩車100米處，還有一輛紅色小汽車尾部有輕微燒過的痕跡。其實，這已非當地近日首次有汽車被縱火，早在11日，一輛白色雪佛蘭（Chevrolet）車也被點燃。<br />\n<br />\n經查，原來4輛車被燒都是一名居住在附近的10歲男童所為，他事後自述點火原因，稱他是因為覺得電視上的爆炸很刺激，好奇之下就點火燒車，想看車爆炸飛起來的畫面。根據內地法律規定，不滿16周歲者放火罪不予刑事處罰，責令家長加以管教，而火災造成的損失由家長或監護人承擔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210428/464106294597390336749351.jpeg/A3f757Pc72HYTOfys_MZ-kcwd-2IwtGWyKBEY8igRGM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210428%2F464106294597390336749351.jpeg%2FA3f757Pc72HYTOfys_MZ-kcwd-2IwtGWyKBEY8igRGM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=d1736fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210428/464108335243726848048519.jpeg/-avIQj8wKsPa2xkdmLs6wNdDwXy5Q8aSm_zV1Jv81dQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210428%2F464108335243726848048519.jpeg%2F-avIQj8wKsPa2xkdmLs6wNdDwXy5Q8aSm_zV1Jv81dQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=cffef002&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210428/464108336921579520926735.jpeg/8wB2oVMXbqHMnW-XzCHXW_74neAXpnW6OR_veDkf73g?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210428%2F464108336921579520926735.jpeg%2F8wB2oVMXbqHMnW-XzCHXW_74neAXpnW6OR_veDkf73g%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fcf69640&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210428/464108338737844224104269.jpeg/N0A99m8y8e5I9wPMXRBVspTHZMycRVHaurdEo7q3RKM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210428%2F464108338737844224104269.jpeg%2FN0A99m8y8e5I9wPMXRBVspTHZMycRVHaurdEo7q3RKM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b114db59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ebbb32db36c5f1036370c6f95eee7776fd8fdb1","tid":2508674,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"玩GTA咪得LOR...<br />\n定係大陸block咗唔比玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89c73a57f771acf61875c6ae198e887ed1c7cb4","tid":2508674,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:47:24.000Z","msg":"呢o的時候緊係燒Telsa, 可以唔使賠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}